Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:25.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(550,550)}亞特羅帕提尼平原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:36.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,100)}帕爾斯國 萬騎長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:36.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(650,0)}{\pos(246,160)}{\fs48}卡蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪 畢竟對殿下來說是初次上陣  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次戰鬥由安德拉寇拉斯陛下親自出陣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將軍巴夫利斯大人也坐鎮於旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且除了我之外
